Package: dtr
Type: Package
Title: Descriptive Tables in the Field of Epidemiology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author@R: as.person("Jeremie Lespinasse <jeremie.lespinasse@outlook.com> [aut, cre]")
Description: A tool to easily inspect data and produce report tables. It provides several
    descriptive statistics for the entire dataset or groups. Statistical comparisons
    either paramatric or not between groups can be added. It provides choices
    to render table in html/pdf within knitr and kableExtra packages or word
    document with flextable package.
License: MIT + file
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tidyr,
    kableExtra
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
